text: Typhoon Yinxing, known as Typhoon Marce in the Philippines, was a category 4 Super Typhoon that hit North Luzon, is a twentieth tropical cyclone in the western Pacific Ocean, And the thirteenth tropical cyclone of annual typhoon names in the Philippines, in the month of November 2024, following by the typhoons of Nika, Ofel and Pepito. ==Meteorological== ===Remained=== On February 2025 PAGASA declared that the name of Marce, remaining from its rotating annual list in 2028, along with Carina. ==Reference== Category:2024 in weather Category:Typhoons in the Philippines Category:Pacific typhoons Category:2024 disasters in Asia
title: Typhoon Yinxing
